high_descs: turn around and walk over to the right of the two bathroom cabinets on the left side of the room
grab the spray bottle off of the cabinet there
turn around and walk over to the right side of the toilet at the end of the room on the left
put the spray bottle on top of the toilet
turn left and walk over to the white cabinet straight ahead
grab the spray bottle off of the cabinet there
turn around and walk over to the toilet at the end of the room
place the spray bottle on top of the toilet next to the other spray bottle
anns.task_desc: place two spray bottles down on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn and go to the small shelf by the toilet.
Pick up a spray bottle on the shelf.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
Turn around and go to the shelf by the sink.
Pick up a spray bottle on the shelf.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the toilet, hang a left and go to the shelf with the spray bottles on it.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle that is on the left.
Turn around and go towards the bathtub, turn to the left, then to the left again and go to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the back of the toilet
Turn around and go to the other side of the room, go to the left to the shelf next to the sink.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle that is on the shelf.
Turn around and go to the other side of the room, turn to the left and go to the toilet.
Put the yellow spray bottle on the back of the toilet to the left of the other yellow spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: turn around, walk to the white box on the left
grab the cleaner at the front
turn around, and turn around, walk to the toilet,
put the cleaner on the toilet
turn left, walk to the white box
grab the cleaner on the box
turn around, walk down to the toilet
put the cleaner on the toilet
anns.task_desc: put the two cleaner bottles from the white box to the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the box against the wall with spray bottles and a bottle of lotion on it.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle closest to you.
Turn around and walk over to the tub, then turn left and walk over to the wall and turn left.
Place the yellow spray bottle on the middle of the toilet tank.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, hang a left after the tub and walk up to the sink, then turn right and walk forward.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle off of the box in front of you.
Turn right and begin walking forward, then turn right again and walk up to the toilet.
Put the yellow spray bottle on top of the toilet tank to the left of the spray bottle that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Go to your right, to the second shelf on the right.
Pick up the front spray bottle.
Carry the bottle to the toilet that is on your right.
Put the bottle on the center of the toilet tank lid.
Face the opposite direction and move forward to the shelf against the wall, to the right of the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle from that shelf.
Turn around to face the toilet and carry the bottle to the toilet.
Put the bottle on the toilet tank lid, to the left of the other bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to the back of the toilet.
